ROTHMAN, Respondent, v. PRUDENTIAL INS. CO., Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. February 28, 1894.) Appeal from ninth district court Action by Max Rothman against the Prudential Insurance Company.

Argued before BISCHOFF and GIEGERICH, JJ.

W. O. Campbell, for appellant. J. L. Weinberg, for respondent

No opinion. Judgment affirmed, with costs.
